<% "Dear #{@member.first_name}," if @member.first_name.present? %>

Thank you for your donation to All Out!

Please note that this gift will appear on your credit card statement as ALLOUT.ORG. All Out is a program of Purpose Action, a 501(c)(4) nonprofit organization.

Your contribution is not tax–deductible. This email certifies that you have made this donation as a charitable contribution and you are not receiving any goods or services in return.

Transaction Information:
<%= "Name: #{@member.first_name} #{@member.last_name}" if @member.first_name.present? && @member.last_name.present? %>
<%= "Postcode: #{@member.postcode}" if @member.postcode.present? %>
<%= "Country: #{@member_country}" unless @member_country.blank? %>
E–mail: <%= @member.email %>
Amount: <%= @transaction_amount %>
Date: <%= @transaction.created_at.strftime("%F") %>
Transaction #:  <%= @transaction.external_id %>

